  <title>GWeather.Provider</title>


<terms>
<item>
<title><code>Provider.NONE</code></title>
  <p>no provider, no weather information available</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>Provider.METAR</code></title>
  <p>METAR office, providing current conditions worldwide</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>Provider.IWIN</code></title>
  <p>US weather office, providing 7 days of forecast</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>Provider.YAHOO</code></title>
  <p>Yahoo Weather Service, worldwide but non commercial only</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>Provider.YR_NO</code></title>
  <p>Yr.no service, worldwide but requires attribution</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>Provider.OWM</code></title>
  <p>OpenWeatherMap, worldwide and possibly more reliable, but requires attribution and is limited in the number of queries</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>Provider.ALL</code></title>
  <p>enable all available providers</p>
</item>
